---
---
<section class="turn" id="the-turn">
  <div class="container--wide">
    <div class="turn__grid">
      <div class="turn__narrative reveal">
        <p class="overline">The Turn</p>
        <hr class="fire-rule" />
        <h2 class="display turn__heading">
          I left early.<br/><em>It was enough.</em>
        </h2>
        <div class="turn__body">
          <p>
            In the military, I got married. I got pregnant. And at four years of service —
            with everything still ahead of me in uniform — I chose a different path.
          </p>
          <p>
            For years, I carried that choice like a wound. The shame of leaving early.
            The grief of an identity I'd poured myself into.
            The question that wouldn't quiet: <em>What would I have become?</em>
          </p>
          <p>
            But honest reckoning rewrites the story. I didn't abandon my service —
            I completed it on my own terms. Every crew I led, every mission I owned,
            every standard I upheld came with me.
            What I carried out of that chapter is worth more than what I left behind.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="cred reveal">
        <div class="cred__item">
          <span class="cred__label">Revenue grown post-military</span>
          <span class="cred__value">560%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cred__item">
          <span class="cred__label">Retention rate achieved</span>
          <span class="cred__value">98%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cred__item">
          <span class="cred__label">Consecutive years Top 10</span>
          <span class="cred__value">4</span>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.turn {
  padding-block: var(--section-pad);
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--coal) 0%, var(--ash) 100%);
  position: relative;
}
.turn::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--crimson), transparent);
}
.turn__grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
  gap: 4rem 5rem;
  align-items: start;
}
.turn__heading {
  font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
  color: var(--white);
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}
.turn__heading em {
  color: var(--flame);
  font-style: italic;
}
.turn__body {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.4rem;
  color: var(--bone);
  opacity: 0.85;
}
.turn__body em {
  color: var(--amber);
  font-style: italic;
}

/* Credential block */
.cred {
  border-left: 2px solid var(--crimson);
  padding-left: 1.75rem;
  position: sticky;
  top: 4rem;
  align-self: start;
}
.cred__item {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.3rem;
  padding-block: 1.25rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(155,127,120,0.12);
}
.cred__item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.cred__label {
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--slate);
}
.cred__value {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--amber);
  line-height: 1.1;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .turn__grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }
  .cred {
    position: static;
  }
}
</style>
